<br>
*Noltrac raises his glass in a toast to all gathered.*<br>
<br>
<br>
*Upon hearing the sound of running feet Noltrac turns grins at the Bouncing Blue Bard who is now standing beside him.*<br>
<br>
&quot;Gwenne! My friend, I must perform the duties expected of a Page for a time. But once that time is done with you and I shall go and find what ever adventure awaits us outside these walls.&quot;<br>
<br>
*Noltrac then takes his position slightly behind and to the right of Racle. His face is serene, but the mad gleam in his eye has been joined by a sparkle of happiness.*<br>
<br>
